snippet.title: Shinseiden Megaseed Fukkatsu-hen PS1 Game Opening Movie.avi
snippet.description:
Opening movie of the PS1 game Shinseiden Megaseed Fukkatsu-hen, a tactical RPG game that was only released in Japan.

Intro del juego de PS1 Shinseiden Megaseed Fukkatsu-hen, un tactico RPG que sólo salió en Japón.

Game copyright: Banpresto (1997)

More information about the game here:
http://www.psxdatacenter.com
